text: pitabrakd nasa puok del brachheang nung a l laoh ning anaknoam sar robsa trong nung trauv ban ke thveu aoy puokke ameasa dauch puok chomnean moun puokke del trauv ban ke thveu aoy ameasa der . haey chea karpit nasa yeung ban banhchouh nouv phosdo tang yeang chbasaleasa . haey samreab puok del kmean chomnue ku tearounakamm yeang ameasa
